latestPosts.caption:
Flaunting my flaws ……
In 2019 i had incident where i got a deep cut above my lips and i was shattered as this society have set standards for beauty. I went into depression thinking my face is ruined now . Nobody will work with me as face is very important in modelling. For 7 months i stopped stepping out of my house . After a while i started getting out but covering my face with full make up and still put mask on my face ( yes i started wearing mask before covid hit ) . It took me whole 2 year to gather the courage to start applying for work opportunities again . And still i wasn’t comfortable posting my face shot as i never had the confidence to show my scar to the world . I would avoid face or closeup pictures as much as possible. But as time passed now i feel this scar is beautiful because i am beautiful this scare has nothing to do with my beauty. My soul is beautiful and for me thats the only thing that matters . 
And these beautiful shot is captured by @siddology 
And the lady that made me feel more beautiful is @palettebydiya2.0 
.
..
…
..
.
[ Face card , dusky beauty, scars are beautiful , self acceptance, gratitude, grateful, foryou ]
